            <title>[LU-17769] Allow test-framework to repeat subtests for a specific duration</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17769</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;To support Autotest running changed subtests for an approximate duration (ATM-2666), the test framework should allow a subtest to be repeated for X minutes. Something like ONLY_REPEAT_MINS=60.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
